#| ": Set the color profile for the display. The option “system display profile” is the preferred setting when working with a calibrated display. The profile is taken either from your system's color manager or from your X display server. The method Ansel uses to detect your system display profile can be changed in [preferences > miscellaneous](../../../preferences-settings/miscellaneous.md). For more information see [display profile](../../../special-topics/color-management/display-profile.md).\n"
