#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"histogram profile\n"
": Set the color profile of the histogram. None of the available options are ideal, however, \"system display profile\" is probably the _least bad_ setting, since all other profiles are derived from the display color space and at least the values will conform to what you see on screen.\n"
