#: content/views/darkroom/modules/lens-correction.md
#: content/views/darkroom/modules/rotate-perspective.md
#: content/views/darkroom/modules/framing.md
#: content/views/darkroom/modules/orientation.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"show guides\n"
": Tick the box to show guide overlays whenever the module is activated. Click the icon on the right to control the properties of the guides. See [guides & overlays](../../toolboxes/guides-overlays.md) for details.\n"
msgstr ""

