#. type: Plain text
#: content/getting-started/library.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Ansel keeps a database of all images it knows, that is all images that were [imported](import.md), until you actively remove them from the library (global menu : _File_ 🡒 _Remove from library_). The library stores the filesystem path of the images, their metadata and their editing history.\n"
