#. type: Plain text
#: content/lua/a-simple-example.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Let's start with a simple example that will print some code on the console. Create a file called `luarc` in Ansel's configuration directory (usually `$HOME/.config/Ansel/`) and add the following line to it:\n"
